03]]\n|4<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2020\"/>\n|\n|-\n! style=\"align: center; background: lavender;\" colspan=\"7\"| [[Electronic-warfare aircraft|Electronic Warfare]]\n|-\n| [[Dassault Falcon 20|Falcon 20]]\n| [[France]]\n| [[Electronic-warfare aircraft|EW]] / [[Radar jamming and deception|radar jamming]]\n|\n| 2<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2020\"/>\n|\n|-\n! style=\"align: center; background: lavender;\" colspan=\"7\" | [[Aerial refueling|Tanker]]\n|-\n| [[Ilyushin Il-78]]\n| [[Russia]]\n|aerial refueling\n|[[Ilyushin Il-78#Variants|Il-78MP]]\n|4<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2020\"/>\n|\n|-\n! style=\"align: center; background: lavender;\" colspan=\"7\" | [[Military transport aircraft|Transport]]\n|-\n| [[Saab 2000]]\n| [[Sweden]]\n| transport \n| \n|6<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2020\"/>\n| \n|-\n| [[Harbin Y-12]]\n| [[China]]\n| transport\n|\n|3<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2020\"/>\n|\n|-\n| [[CASA/IPTN CN-235|CASA CN-235]]\n|[[Spain]] / [[Indonesia]]\n| transport\n|\n| 3<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2020\"/>\n|\n|-\n|[[Lockheed C-130 Hercules|C-130 Hercules]]\n|[[United States]]\n|transport\n|[[Lockheed C-130 Hercules#Variants|C-130B/E/]]/[[Lockheed L-100 Hercules|L-100]]\n| 16<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2020\"/>\n|\n|-\n! style=\"align: center; background: lavender;\" colspan=\"7\" | [[Helicopters]]\n|-\n|[[Bell 412]]\n|[[United States]]\n|utility \n|\n|1<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2020\"/>\n| \n|-\n|[[Bell UH-1 Iroquois|Bell UH-1]]\n| [[United States]]\n|utility \n|\n|5<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2020\"/>\n|\n|-\n| [[Mil Mi-17]]\n| [[Russia]]\n| [[Utility helicopter|utility]]\n|[[Mil Mi-17#Variants|Mi-17/171]]\n| 6<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2020\"/>\n|\n|-\n|[[Bell AH-1 Cobra|AH-1 Cobra]]\n| [[United States]]\n|attack \n|[[Bell AH-1 Cobra#Variants|AH-1F]]\n|1<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2020\"/>\n|\n|-\n|[[A\u00e9rospatiale SA 330 Puma|A\u00e9rospatiale SA330]]\n|[[France]]\n|utility / transport \n|\n|1<ref name=\"World Air Forces 2020\"/>\n|\n|-\n|[[A\u0